Download Virtual Master from Google Play. https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.clone.android.dual.space


Download Zarchiver from Google Play.
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ru.zdevs.zarchiver


After completing the basic setup for Virtual Master, create a virtual machine with Android 7.


Next, import the Zarchiver application you downloaded into the emulator.


Install the APK file located in the Real Racing 3 game folder.


Place the game's data file in the following directory.
üëáüèª

Android/data/com.ea.games.r3_row

Disconnect the emulator from the internet, and if possible, disconnect the device from the internet as well. The game should not be connected to the internet.
